title: The Great Adventure- A Journey Through the Bible
description: A Quick Journey through the Bible is an 8-part introduction to the Bible Timeline learning system.  This study is designed to give the student a brief overview of salvation history, from Genesis through the resurrection of Christ and the establishment of the Catholic Church.  Students will learn about the spiritual benefits of Bible study and how to enter deeper into "His-story" as they begin their study of the Scriptures.
